snippet.textDisplay: I can't believe I just came back from Medina last week. I was thinking of this naat on my way there. I hope my salam was accepted by the prophet and I can practice the humility, kindness and softness of our Prophet SM's character in my daily life. I also pray all mumeen gets to visit his rawjah at least once in lifetime, it's a goosbump moment to be near his(pbuh) grave, to be literally in Riyazul Jannah (heaven's garden)!!  Medina is the most peaceful city, it heals and softened your heart and also reminds you of our Prophet SM's humble personality.
